  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">This Privacy Policy explains how Norway Card Advisor (referred to as "we", "us" or "our") collects, uses and safeguards personal information. We are committed to protecting your privacy and complying with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Norwegian data protection laws.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We collect minimal information necessary to operate the website and provide services to you. This may include your email address when you sign up for newsletters, technical data such as browser type and IP address for analytics, and preferences saved via cookies.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
      <li>To operate and maintain the website.</li>
      <li>To send you newsletters and updates if you have subscribed.</li>
      <li>To analyse website usage using anonymised analytics to improve our services.</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Cookies are small text files stored on your device. We use essential cookies to remember your preferences, and optional analytics or marketing cookies only after obtaining your consent via our cookie banner. You can revoke or change your consent at any time via the cookie settings link in the banner.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Data Retention</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We retain personal data only as long as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. You may contact us to request deletion of your personal information.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Under the GDPR you have the right to access, rectify or erase your personal data, restrict or object to processing and request data portability. To exercise these rights please contact us at <a href="mailto:info@example.com" class="text-accent underline">info@example.com</a>.</p>
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via the details provided on our <a href="/contact" class="text-accent underline">contact page</a>.</p>
  </section>
